<i>Animal characters made by CG</i>

18
00:02:10,810 --> 00:02:11,650
Hongyu!

19
00:02:13,210 --> 00:02:14,440
Be careful. Don’t scare it.

20
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:19,600
<i>Animal characters made by CG</i>

21
00:02:19,610 --> 00:02:21,810
Finally, I got you!

22
00:02:21,810 --> 00:02:22,850
Let go of Hongyu.

23
00:02:22,850 --> 00:02:23,790
You hurt it.

24
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,240
<i>Animal characters made by CG</i>

25
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:28,130
Let me have it for a couple of days.

26
00:02:28,810 --> 00:02:29,850
Bonehead!

27
00:02:29,850 --> 00:02:30,560
What?

28
00:02:34,740 --> 00:02:36,020
Li Sheng?

29
00:02:36,020 --> 00:02:37,610
You hurt me!

30
00:02:38,170 --> 00:02:40,020
You feel it?

31
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:42,570
I heard you shouting far away.

32
00:02:42,570 --> 00:02:43,740
Tell me.

33
00:02:43,740 --> 00:02:45,330
Why are you here?

34
00:02:47,330 --> 00:02:48,620
He took me here.

35
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:49,690
Me?

36
00:02:49,690 --> 00:02:50,970
Nonsense!

37
00:02:51,460 --> 00:02:53,320
Who would bring a burden like you?

38
00:02:54,210 --> 00:02:55,050
Burden?

39
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:56,460
You all take me as a burden.

40
00:02:56,460 --> 00:02:58,380
But he doesn’t!

41
00:02:58,380 --> 00:02:59,770
He asked me to lead the way for him.

42
00:02:59,770 --> 00:03:01,460
That’s why I come to the Assembly.

43
00:03:01,460 --> 00:03:02,260
Right?

44
00:03:04,660 --> 00:03:05,770
Let go of her.

45
00:03:05,770 --> 00:03:07,050
She saved my life.

46
00:03:07,050 --> 00:03:08,570
She’s a heroine
with the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

47
00:03:08,570 --> 00:03:09,410
You can’t do this to her.

48
00:03:09,410 --> 00:03:10,100
Let go of her.

49
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:11,540
Heroine?

50
00:03:12,020 --> 00:03:13,190
I’m her brother.

51
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:20,820
You... You!

52
00:03:20,820 --> 00:03:22,820
You’re Li Yan

53
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:25,130
who ran away this morning?

54
00:03:26,460 --> 00:03:27,410
Wait.

55
00:03:27,410 --> 00:03:28,660
Why are you coming behind me?

56
00:03:28,660 --> 00:03:30,540
Because when we came this morning...

57
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:32,300
All right. All right.

58
00:03:32,300 --> 00:03:33,970
Let’s not stand here or argue.

59
00:03:33,970 --> 00:03:36,210
We’re lost. Let’s go find a way out.

60
00:03:38,620 --> 00:03:40,210
I’ll deal with you later.

61
00:03:42,260 --> 00:03:43,410
That’s it.

62
00:03:43,410 --> 00:03:45,130
You’ve returned the favor. We’re even.

63
00:03:45,130 --> 00:03:46,460
Give Hongyu back to me.

64
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:48,300
Let me have it for a couple of days.

65
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:50,900
When I just walked into the forest,

66
00:03:50,900 --> 00:03:53,100
I realized it was designed
according to Qi Men Dun Jia Formation.

67
00:03:53,100 --> 00:03:55,180
It can stop everyone except me.

68
00:03:55,180 --> 00:03:55,740
Come with me.

69
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:15,460
Seems like we started off early,

70
00:04:15,460 --> 00:04:17,130
but arrived late.

71
00:04:18,130 --> 00:04:19,130
Tortoise Master.

72
00:04:19,130 --> 00:04:21,460
Here comes the girl
with the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

73
00:04:24,690 --> 00:04:26,490
You’re the girl

74
00:04:26,490 --> 00:04:28,460
who interfered in Lingling Inn, right?

75
00:04:29,210 --> 00:04:31,210
Who are you?

76
00:04:31,690 --> 00:04:32,900
No matter how naughty

77
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:34,900
my subordinates were,

78
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:37,490
you had no right to teach them a lesson.

79
00:04:37,490 --> 00:04:39,740
Why do you think you can ask who I am?

80
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:41,660
Want a fight?

81
00:04:52,410 --> 00:04:53,900
Tortoise Master,

82
00:04:53,900 --> 00:04:56,340
I don’t think you come to take revenge,
do you?

83
00:04:57,650 --> 00:05:00,530
Well, this beautiful girl sounds nice.

84
00:05:00,530 --> 00:05:02,060
Why was it so disgusting

85
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:02,900
when he said the word beautiful?

86
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:04,020
Fine.

87
00:05:04,020 --> 00:05:06,220
I’ll get even with you

88
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:07,850
for what happened in Lingling Inn

89
00:05:07,850 --> 00:05:10,850
after the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

90
00:05:13,650 --> 00:05:16,530
Uh, that pavilion looks nice.

91
00:05:16,530 --> 00:05:18,130
Let’s go over there.

92
00:05:18,130 --> 00:05:19,570
Fei, go.

93
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:22,620
Go.

94
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:54,850
Look at it.

95
00:05:54,850 --> 00:05:56,780
Is this the Assembly of Martial Artists

96
00:05:56,780 --> 00:05:59,500
or the Malicious Banquet?

97
00:05:59,500 --> 00:06:02,060
Those with invitations have been taken
to the waterside pavilion.

98
00:06:02,060 --> 00:06:04,460
Those without invitations
are here with us.

99
00:06:04,460 --> 00:06:05,570
No wonder

100
00:06:05,570 --> 00:06:07,340
Huo Liantao wrote names
on the invitations.

101
00:06:09,090 --> 00:06:10,940
When I was in the dungeon
of the Huo family,

102
00:06:10,940 --> 00:06:12,130
I realized that

103
00:06:12,130 --> 00:06:13,740
Huo Liantao thought strangely.

104
00:06:13,740 --> 00:06:15,810
We can’t estimate him in a normal way.

105
00:06:22,130 --> 00:06:23,580
Turns out he only sent invitations
to his supporters.

106
00:06:24,690 --> 00:06:25,850
Everybody.

107
00:06:26,300 --> 00:06:28,740
Thank you for coming.

108
00:06:28,740 --> 00:06:30,780
It is my great honor!

109
00:06:31,370 --> 00:06:32,940
I’m so grateful!

110
00:06:32,940 --> 00:06:34,810
So grateful!

111
00:06:34,810 --> 00:06:36,340
People always say

112
00:06:36,340 --> 00:06:38,410
our martial world is declining

113
00:06:38,410 --> 00:06:41,570
where there’s no leader
for martial artists

114
00:06:41,570 --> 00:06:43,530
and there are no real heroes.

115
00:06:43,530 --> 00:06:45,530
That’s nonsense!

116
00:06:45,530 --> 00:06:48,900
Today, I gather you here,

117
00:06:48,900 --> 00:06:50,970
just to persuade you

118
00:06:50,970 --> 00:06:53,180
to get rid of prejudice
against different sects

119
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:55,090
and make concerted efforts

120
00:06:55,090 --> 00:06:56,740
with each other!

121
00:06:56,740 --> 00:06:57,970
Today,

122
00:06:57,970 --> 00:06:59,970
if we can find a real hero

123
00:06:59,970 --> 00:07:01,850
among so many people

124
00:07:01,850 --> 00:07:03,810
to command the martial world,

125
00:07:04,370 --> 00:07:06,690
<i>Auspicious Omen and Luck</i>
I will follow him

126
00:07:06,690 --> 00:07:09,250
and give him my heirloom!

127
00:07:09,250 --> 00:07:11,690
Heirloom? So generous?

128
00:07:16,690 --> 00:07:18,740
Why is Huo Liantao suddenly so generous?

129
00:07:18,740 --> 00:07:20,650
Does he really know
what the ripple pattern is?

130
00:07:20,650 --> 00:07:22,340
The rumor has spread all over the towns.

131
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:24,970
If he still didn’t know
what the Color of Ocean and Heaven was,

132
00:07:24,970 --> 00:07:26,650
I’m afraid

133
00:07:26,650 --> 00:07:28,940
his brain could be a stupid chamber pot.

134
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:30,130
This is what we carved

135
00:07:30,130 --> 00:07:33,340
on the Seal of Cautiousness.

136
00:07:33,340 --> 00:07:34,570
This seal is the object,

137
00:07:34,570 --> 00:07:37,460
representing the master of our sect.

138
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:39,970
I’ve been ignorant for years.

139
00:07:39,970 --> 00:07:41,370
Not until recently

140
00:07:41,370 --> 00:07:44,220
did I know the greatness of the pattern.

141
00:07:44,620 --> 00:07:46,810
Demons are running amuck everywhere.

142
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:48,970
I know how slight my talent is.

143
00:07:48,970 --> 00:07:50,530
I want to find a talented man out of you

144
00:07:50,530 --> 00:07:53,570
to take over the Seal of Cautiousness

145
00:07:53,570 --> 00:07:55,740
so that we can find

146
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:57,340
the Color of Ocean and Heaven

147
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:58,940
and fight against Demons together!

148
00:07:59,530 --> 00:08:04,650
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

149
00:08:04,850 --> 00:08:06,090
Is Huo Liantao really so good

150
00:08:06,090 --> 00:08:07,620
at persuading people?

151
00:08:07,620 --> 00:08:09,940
No wonder even Phoenix Master
was bought over.

152
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:12,060
This is the confidence and charm

153
00:08:12,060 --> 00:08:13,530
to call on everyone.

154
00:08:14,130 --> 00:08:15,740
When you learn a little bit,

155
00:08:15,740 --> 00:08:18,090
you can deceive people with it.

156
00:08:24,030 --> 00:08:27,590
Master Huo doesn’t look like a bad man.

157
00:08:27,590 --> 00:08:29,990
Will he really pick a master
of the Martial World?

158
00:08:29,990 --> 00:08:31,120
Martial arts Huo Liantao has

159
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:33,400
are not half as good
as Old Master Huo’s.

160
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:34,800
I really wonder

161
00:08:34,800 --> 00:08:36,360
who taught him the deceiving skills.

162
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,750
The best way to deceive people

163
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:41,030
is to tell the truth and lies together.

164
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:43,200
Unlike someone

165
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:45,080
who makes up everything

166
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,120
and sounds obviously deceptive.

167
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:49,150
She can fool no one, but idiots.

168
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:52,470
Seems like you’ve got a lot to learn.

169
00:08:53,710 --> 00:08:55,990
Who...? Who is the idiot?

170
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:59,310
Huo Liantao, are you telling the truth?

171
00:08:59,310 --> 00:09:01,430
Well, pick our Tortoise Master, then!

172
00:09:01,430 --> 00:09:03,310
Give us the Seal!

173
00:09:03,310 --> 00:09:06,590
-Pick Tortoise Master!
-Pick Tortoise Master!

174
00:09:06,590 --> 00:09:09,200
-Pick Tortoise Master!
-Pick Tortoise Master!

175
00:09:09,750 --> 00:09:10,840
When he appeared,

176
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,750
he showed the ripple pattern

177
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:14,990
and said it was the heirloom
of his family.

178
00:09:14,990 --> 00:09:16,640
What exactly does he want?

179
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:19,640
Demons have kept an eye on him.

180
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:20,870
Besides, he offended many men

181
00:09:20,870 --> 00:09:22,110
in the dungeon.

182
00:09:22,110 --> 00:09:23,310
He didn’t have a choice,

183
00:09:23,310 --> 00:09:25,400
but to expose
the Color of Ocean and Heaven

184
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:27,550
and see who wants to take over the Seal.

185
00:09:27,550 --> 00:09:28,600
In this way,

186
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,280
he can draw the Demons’ attention off.

187
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,840
I think there’s more of it.

188
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,080
I guess

189
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,430
Huo Liantao is up to something else.

190
00:09:34,430 --> 00:09:35,990
Why must we pick him
as the Master of Martial World?

191
00:09:35,990 --> 00:09:37,310
Does he deserve it?

192
00:09:37,310 --> 00:09:38,790
Come and compete if you dare!

193
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:40,640
Let’s decide with our martial arts.

194
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,550
Fine, then!

195
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:43,280
Come on. Come up.

196
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,670
Master Huo!

197
00:09:44,670 --> 00:09:46,280
We all know

198
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:48,350
the ripple pattern is extraordinary.

199
00:09:48,350 --> 00:09:49,960
But do you know

200
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:52,720
what the Color of Ocean and Heaven

201
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,520
truly represents?

202
00:09:55,990 --> 00:09:57,990
The treasure is known

203
00:09:57,990 --> 00:09:59,840
as the Color of Ocean and Heaven.

204
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:02,110
During the mutiny of the former dynasty,

205
00:10:02,110 --> 00:10:04,110
all martial artists felt insecure.

206
00:10:04,110 --> 00:10:06,080
Demons used dirty tricks

207
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,040
to persecute the faithful men!

208
00:10:08,790 --> 00:10:10,520
Over the past few years,

209
00:10:11,430 --> 00:10:13,520
many relics of heroes

210
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:16,480
and many achievements of masters

211
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:18,720
would be ruined

212
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:21,230
in the calamity.

213
00:10:21,230 --> 00:10:25,160
Then my brother contacted many people

214
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:27,080
to fight side by side,

215
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,520
including Mr. Yin Wenlan, Mr. Li Zheng,

216
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:30,750
and seniors of Qi School.

217
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:32,040
Led by my brother,

218
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:33,350
they formed an alliance,

219
00:10:33,350 --> 00:10:34,960
known as the Color of Ocean and Heaven.

220
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:37,280
It was set up,

221
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:38,480
to rescue orphans of different sects

222
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,870
and protect their relics.

223
00:10:39,870 --> 00:10:43,160
The Color of Ocean and Heaven is
the hope to recover the martial world.

224
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:44,960
Whoever has it will master the world.

225
00:10:45,310 --> 00:10:48,280
To get it, Demons attacked Yin’s Mansion
several times

226
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:50,430
and massacred
the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

227
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,750
Even people with Qi School

228
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:53,310
stayed in seclusion.

229
00:10:53,310 --> 00:10:57,040
You can imagine how powerful
the Color of Ocean and Heaven is!

230
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:58,160
What did I tell you?

231
00:10:58,160 --> 00:10:59,790
Huo Liantao failed to figure out

232
00:10:59,790 --> 00:11:01,670
what the Color of Ocean and Heaven was.

233
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:02,640
Then, he pretended he knew it

234
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:04,200
and held the Assembly.

235
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,350
How did you know he figured out nothing?

236
00:11:06,350 --> 00:11:07,960
Because he’s made up
a similar story to mine.

237
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,110
Made up?

238
00:11:09,110 --> 00:11:10,400
Fei.

239
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:12,350
What did you tell Yang Jin?

240
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:16,350
How... How bad you are!

241
00:11:16,350 --> 00:11:17,720
Bonehead, calm down.

242
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,600
I...

243
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,160
If you act on impulse again,

244
00:11:20,160 --> 00:11:21,960
I’ll ask Hongyu to bite you.

245
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:25,670
You’re from the south.

246
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:27,040
Why are you scared of a snake?

247
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:28,670
I’m even scared of coldness.

248
00:11:28,670 --> 00:11:30,870
Be nice to Hongyu.

249
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:32,430
Don’t bully it.

250
00:11:45,350 --> 00:11:46,420
Stop, all of you!

251
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:49,280
Your Highness.

252
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,520
Something feels wrong.

253
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:52,200
Stop moving forward.

254
00:11:57,990 --> 00:12:02,040
You must be the Third Prince.

255
00:12:05,350 --> 00:12:06,990
I’ve heard a lot about you.

256
00:12:07,520 --> 00:12:08,870
Very good!

257
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:10,160
Master Huo.

258
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:12,670
What you said sounds great.

259
00:12:12,670 --> 00:12:14,870
Whoever hears it can take part.

260
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:17,480
I’d like to do something.

261
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:19,640
Let me be the Master of Martial World

262
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:23,600
and take over the Seal of Cautiousness.

263
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:25,720
Junior Master Huo.

264
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,350
Like you just said,

265
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:29,430
we’re having the Assembly today.

266
00:12:29,430 --> 00:12:30,910
Since so,

267
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:32,960
we should compete in martial arts.

268
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,480
Who has the best martial arts

269
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:36,280
can get the Seal of Cautiousness!

270
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,550
Without the competition,

271
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:39,110
why do you think you can get the Seal?

272
00:12:39,110 --> 00:12:42,910
-Yeah!
-Without the competition,

273
00:12:42,910 --> 00:12:44,430
why do you think you can get the Seal?

274
00:12:44,430 --> 00:12:45,350
Everybody.

275
00:12:45,350 --> 00:12:48,310
Show some mercy in the competition.

276
00:12:48,310 --> 00:12:50,550
Don’t kill each other.

277
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:51,600
