00:40:07,350 --> 00:40:08,040
He made up the lie

837
00:40:08,040 --> 00:40:10,480
to deceive all the heroes!

838
00:40:10,480 --> 00:40:11,870
He’s making me

839
00:40:11,870 --> 00:40:14,560
a heartless man, isn’t he?

840
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:16,720
Huo Liantao!

841
00:40:16,870 --> 00:40:18,720
I never expected that!

842
00:40:18,720 --> 00:40:19,910
How shameless you are!

843
00:40:19,910 --> 00:40:21,480
You colluded with the Demons.

844
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:23,240
You even abandoned your own brother!

845
00:40:23,240 --> 00:40:24,520
Tell me.

846
00:40:24,520 --> 00:40:25,870
Who made you brave enough

847
00:40:25,870 --> 00:40:26,520
to stand here

848
00:40:26,520 --> 00:40:28,520
and call yourself Master Huo?

849
00:40:28,520 --> 00:40:30,110
Colluded with the Demons?

850
00:40:30,110 --> 00:40:31,260
What does that mean?

851
00:40:32,430 --> 00:40:33,500
Lord Chu.

852
00:40:33,870 --> 00:40:36,590
I guess you don’t work
for the Third Prince,

853
00:40:36,590 --> 00:40:38,640
but for Lord Shen of Demons Manor.

854
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,560
Handsome boy.

855
00:40:43,560 --> 00:40:44,960
It’s been days.

856
00:40:44,960 --> 00:40:46,480
You’ve made much progress.

857
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:49,140
You recognized him, too?

858
00:40:49,720 --> 00:40:51,390
He is Chu Tianyu,

859
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:55,300
a lackey with Demons Manor.

860
00:40:56,040 --> 00:40:58,110
Why do they turn up

861
00:40:58,110 --> 00:40:59,800
wherever there’s news
about the Color of Ocean and Heaven?

862
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:02,560
Just like dogs after meat.

863
00:41:02,560 --> 00:41:03,830
Shame on them!

864
00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:06,280
Huo Liantao.

865
00:41:06,280 --> 00:41:08,200
How dare you collude with the Demons!

866
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:09,560
Everybody.

867
00:41:09,560 --> 00:41:11,070
Everybody, let me explain!

868
00:41:11,070 --> 00:41:11,760
Let me explain!

869
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:13,110
Collude?

870
00:41:13,110 --> 00:41:14,590
What a joke!

871
00:41:15,760 --> 00:41:16,670
Huo Liantao is nothing,

872
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:20,150
but a dog of mine!

873
00:41:20,150 --> 00:41:20,850
I...

874
00:41:21,430 --> 00:41:22,670
Seems like

875
00:41:22,670 --> 00:41:24,350
Chu Tianyu will fall out
with Huo Liantao

876
00:41:24,350 --> 00:41:25,500
before killing people with his help.

877
00:41:28,830 --> 00:41:30,110
Liantao.

878
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:32,480
I knew you were stupid
since you were little.

879
00:41:32,480 --> 00:41:33,830
After so many years,

880
00:41:33,830 --> 00:41:35,350
I didn’t expect you

881
00:41:35,350 --> 00:41:37,560
to have learnt nothing!

882
00:41:38,240 --> 00:41:40,430
You are as stupid as you were.

883
00:41:40,760 --> 00:41:42,960
You collude with the Demons!

884
00:41:43,590 --> 00:41:45,430
I can’t help suspecting

885
00:41:45,430 --> 00:41:47,240
how your brother died.

886
00:41:47,630 --> 00:41:49,620
How was he poisoned?

887
00:41:50,520 --> 00:41:51,960
That time...

888
00:41:51,960 --> 00:41:54,560
I hadn’t colluded with the Demons
back at that time.

889
00:41:57,520 --> 00:41:58,470
Master.

890
00:42:00,280 --> 00:42:01,300
He acknowledged it.

891
00:42:01,720 --> 00:42:04,390
I’m afraid
there’ll be a desperate fight.

892
00:42:04,390 --> 00:42:06,280
Fei, I’m serious.

893
00:42:06,280 --> 00:42:07,960
Unlock me. I won’t run away.

894
00:42:11,350 --> 00:42:12,960
I acknowledge

895
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:14,150
what Qian Xiaoliu said.

896
00:42:14,150 --> 00:42:16,520
But... The poison...

897
00:42:16,520 --> 00:42:18,520
It wasn’t me.

898
00:42:18,520 --> 00:42:20,070
Poison?

899
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:23,200
However heartless I was,

900
00:42:23,200 --> 00:42:25,390
I wouldn’t poison my own brother!

901
00:42:25,390 --> 00:42:27,000
Old Master Huo

902
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:29,670
was poisoned?

903
00:42:31,320 --> 00:42:33,560
Among the Demons,

904
00:42:33,560 --> 00:42:35,420
only Pathetic Clam could
poison Old Master Huo.

905
00:42:36,390 --> 00:42:37,830
Sheng! Sheng!

906
00:42:37,830 --> 00:42:38,240
Bad news!

907
00:42:38,240 --> 00:42:39,800
Someone is lighting a fire
in the forest!

908
00:42:39,800 --> 00:42:42,480
On fire? On fire?

909
00:42:42,480 --> 00:42:44,200
On fire? Go. Hurry.

910
00:42:44,200 --> 00:42:46,630
Run! Go!

911
00:42:47,110 --> 00:42:49,110
Huo Liantao, don’t try to run away!

912
00:42:49,430 --> 00:42:50,640
Stop!

913
00:42:55,480 --> 00:42:58,040
Screwed! There’s all kerosene
in the forest!

914
00:42:59,110 --> 00:43:00,200
Fei, hurry.

915
00:43:00,200 --> 00:43:01,150
Chu Tianyu is running away.

916
00:43:01,520 --> 00:43:02,480
Don’t move.

917
00:43:02,480 --> 00:43:04,240
Miss Zhou. Miss Zhou.

918
00:43:08,800 --> 00:43:09,870
Miss Zhou.

919
00:43:09,870 --> 00:43:11,730
Go!

920
00:43:12,240 --> 00:43:13,480
Zichen ran towards the back
of the mansion.

921
00:43:13,480 --> 00:43:14,430
Let’s go pick him up.

922
00:43:21,240 --> 00:43:22,560
Give me the Seal!

923
00:43:22,760 --> 00:43:24,070
Catch him!

924
00:43:24,800 --> 00:43:25,680
<i>Huo</i>

925
00:43:27,000 --> 00:43:27,400
<i>Sparrow</i>

926
00:43:40,000 --> 00:43:41,590
Wanna run?

927
00:44:17,150 --> 00:44:18,110
Bonehead.

928
00:44:19,000 --> 00:44:20,350
Finally, you’re back.

929
00:44:20,350 --> 00:44:21,350
Are you alright?

930
00:44:21,350 --> 00:44:22,830
You’re here. I’d certainly come back!

931
00:44:22,830 --> 00:44:24,590
I made marks all the way.

932
00:44:24,910 --> 00:44:25,720
Yang Jin.

933
00:44:25,960 --> 00:44:27,350
Take Chuchu and Yan

934
00:44:27,350 --> 00:44:28,200
out of the forest

935
00:44:28,200 --> 00:44:29,480
by following Hongyu.

936
00:44:29,480 --> 00:44:30,240
What about you?

937
00:44:30,240 --> 00:44:31,150
I must go back.

938
00:44:31,150 --> 00:44:32,280
Those martial artists can’t come out,

939
00:44:32,280 --> 00:44:33,590
unless someone leads the way.

940
00:44:33,590 --> 00:44:34,480
Let me help you.

941
00:44:34,480 --> 00:44:35,670
Two girls and a snake.

942
00:44:35,670 --> 00:44:36,720
Don’t you worry about them?

943
00:44:39,240 --> 00:44:40,200
Well, be very careful, then.

944
00:44:41,870 --> 00:44:42,720
Sheng.

945
00:44:43,910 --> 00:44:44,760
Be careful.

946
00:44:52,910 --> 00:44:53,830
Uh... Uh...

947
00:44:53,830 --> 00:44:54,830
Why are we back

948
00:44:54,830 --> 00:44:56,150
after going around?

949
00:44:56,150 --> 00:44:57,520
You misled us
when you didn’t know the way.

950
00:44:57,520 --> 00:44:58,830
Go to hell!

951
00:44:59,350 --> 00:45:00,390
Stop!

952
00:45:04,590 --> 00:45:05,390
Tortoise Master.

953
00:45:05,830 --> 00:45:08,280
We’re in the same trouble.

954
00:45:08,280 --> 00:45:09,670
Let’s get out of this place first.

955
00:45:09,670 --> 00:45:11,960
He wasted so much time.

956
00:45:11,960 --> 00:45:13,670
What if I insist on killing him?

957
00:45:13,670 --> 00:45:15,320
Tortoise Master.

958
00:45:15,320 --> 00:45:17,960
You really can’t
distinguish the right from the wrong.

959
00:45:17,960 --> 00:45:19,200
Do you really want to reject me

960
00:45:19,200 --> 00:45:20,000
and trap everyone in this forest

961
00:45:20,000 --> 00:45:22,110
filled with kerosene?

962
00:45:23,200 --> 00:45:24,200
Uh...

963
00:45:24,320 --> 00:45:26,280
Are you so eager to be a public enemy?

964
00:45:28,240 --> 00:45:29,630
Public enemy?

965
00:45:30,110 --> 00:45:31,350
Of whom?

966
00:45:31,760 --> 00:45:34,200
Weak men like you?

967
00:45:34,830 --> 00:45:36,670
Mr. Li.

968
00:45:36,670 --> 00:45:39,240
I haven’t asked you
for the Color of Ocean and Heaven yet.

969
00:45:39,240 --> 00:45:40,560
Can’t you see that?

970
00:45:40,560 --> 00:45:42,110
Who has the Color of Ocean and Heaven

971
00:45:42,110 --> 00:45:44,150
will be the public enemy.

972
00:45:44,150 --> 00:45:45,150
Shut your mouth.

973
00:45:45,150 --> 00:45:46,520
Flies have got in.

974
00:45:47,320 --> 00:45:49,760
Fine. If anyone wants the treasure,

975
00:45:49,760 --> 00:45:51,320
kill me now.

976
00:45:51,320 --> 00:45:52,480
If anyone wants to live,

977
00:45:52,480 --> 00:45:53,430
follow me!

978
00:45:58,040 --> 00:45:59,390
Mr. Li?

979
00:45:59,390 --> 00:46:01,430
When I met you in Lingling Inn,

980
00:46:01,430 --> 00:46:02,960
I was too busy to say hello.

981
00:46:03,430 --> 00:46:05,350
You’re Li Zheng’s grandson?

982
00:46:07,670 --> 00:46:09,110
You can walk through the forest?

983
00:46:09,760 --> 00:46:10,560
Yes.

984
00:46:11,480 --> 00:46:12,800
I learnt some Qi Men Dun Jia skills

985
00:46:12,800 --> 00:46:14,560
from Mr. Chongxiao.

986
00:46:14,560 --> 00:46:16,790
Fine! I’ll go with you.

987
00:46:18,040 --> 00:46:20,150
Follow us if you want to live.

988
00:46:20,150 --> 00:46:21,390
Otherwise,

989
00:46:21,390 --> 00:46:23,390
stay and wait to die!

990
00:46:23,660 --> 00:46:24,800
Let’s go.

991
00:46:25,040 --> 00:46:27,110
Who dares to leave before I agree?

992
00:46:27,590 --> 00:46:29,350
Take them out first.

